69
00:04:59,710 --> 00:05:01,030
So, and let me say,

70
00:05:01,030 --> 00:05:06,570
I changed the frequency of
the trap as I just showed you.

71
00:05:06,570 --> 00:05:08,450
What happens is that these particles,

72
00:05:08,450 --> 00:05:13,540
which used to be in the ground state of
the old potential, now get redistributed

73
00:05:13,540 --> 00:05:18,790
to, essentially,
all possible states of the new potential.

74
00:05:18,790 --> 00:05:20,720
And after time goes by, so

75
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:24,700
there is some relaxation going on, and
the system relaxes to a new state, but

76
00:05:24,700 --> 00:05:26,690
now the temperature of the state
is going to be larger.

77
00:05:26,690 --> 00:05:29,700
The temperature is actually
essentially the measure

78
00:05:29,700 --> 00:05:32,590
