Now, so now let me move,
actually, to a similar but

104
00:07:16,208 --> 00:07:22,160
physically quite different problem,
which also involves sudden perturbation,

105
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:26,340
but it's a perturbation of
a completely different type.

106
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:32,300
So the toy problem that we're going
to solve was actually a serious

107
00:07:32,300 --> 00:07:36,590
research problem back 70 years ago or

108
00:07:36,590 --> 00:07:40,750
so in the good old days
of theoretical physics.

109
00:07:40,750 --> 00:07:45,671
And it was, actually, considered by a
