00:12:59,451 --> 00:13:02,827
a higher energy state is,
let's say some other state.

191
00:13:02,827 --> 00:13:09,112
I'm not going to specify what it is but
some, let's say psi sub k, whatever k is.

192
00:13:09,112 --> 00:13:13,680
k could be a collection of indices,
involving the radial quantum numbers and

